The paper discusses a technique to increase the effective memory capacity and bandwidth of GPUs for HPC and DL workloads. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories related to these fields, such as Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions compression techniques, which could fall under the sub-category of Architecture (cs.AR).
